<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profil simplifié</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/profile.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <header class="main-header">
        <h1>SPORT-HUB</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/profile" class="active">Profil</a>
            <a href="/">Acceuil</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="user-profile">
        <div class="profile-main">
            <div class="profile-pic-container">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Photo de profil" id="profile-pic">
                <div class="change-photo">
                    <label for="photo-upload">
                        <i class="fas fa-camera"></i>
                    </label>
                    <input type="file" id="photo-upload" accept="image/*">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="profile-info">
                <h1 class="display-name">Tom Pass</h1>
                <p class="username">@tompass8</p>

                <p class="location-join">
                    <span><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Membre depuis mai 2022</span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="posts-section">
        <h2>Mes posts</h2>

        <div class="create-post">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" alt="Photo de profil">
            <textarea placeholder="Quoi de neuf ?"></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Poster</button>
        </div>

        <div class="posts-list">
            <div class="post">
                <div class="post-header">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" alt="Photo de profil">
                    <div class="post-user">
                        <span class="post-name">Tom Pass</span>
                        <span class="post-username">@tompass8</span>
                        <span class="post-time">· 2h</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="post-content">
                    <p>Je viens de terminer un nouveau projet passionnant ! #developpement #webdesign</p>
                </div>

                <div class="post-actions">
                    <button><i class="far fa-heart"></i> <span>47</span></button>
                    <button class="comment-btn"><i class="far fa-comment"></i> <span>5</span></button>
                </div>

                <div class="comments-section">
                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="Photo commentateur">
                        <div class="comment-content">
                            <p><strong>Marc D.</strong> <span>@marc_d</span></p>
                            <p>Super projet ! J'ai hâte d'en voir plus.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="add-comment">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="Photo de profil">
                        <textarea placeholder="Ajouter un commentaire..."></textarea>
                        <button>Commenter</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="post">
                <div class="post-header">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" alt="Photo de profil">
                    <div class="post-user">
                        <span class="post-name">Tom Pass</span>
                        <span class="post-username">@tompass8</span>
                        <span class="post-time">· 1j</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="post-content">
                    <p>Les nouvelles fonctionnalités de CSS sont incroyables ! J'ai hâte de les utiliser dans mes
                        prochains projets. #CSS #WebDev</p>
                </div>

                <div class="post-actions">
                    <button><i class="far fa-heart"></i> <span>76</span></button>
                    <button class="comment-btn"><i class="far fa-comment"></i> <span>8</span></button>
                </div>

                <div class="comments-section hidden">
                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="Photo commentateur">
                        <div class="comment-content">
                            <p><strong>Sophie L.</strong> <span>@sophieL</span></p>
                            <p>La communication régulière est la clé ! Des standups quotidiens courts et efficaces.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="comment">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="Photo commentateur">
                        <div class="comment-content">
                            <p><strong>Jean M.</strong> <span>@jeanm</span></p>
                            <p>Utiliser des outils comme Trello ou Notion pour suivre les tâches.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="add-comment">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/40" alt="Photo de profil">
                        <textarea placeholder="Ajouter un commentaire..."></textarea>
                        <button>Commenter</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 SPORT-HUB - Version 1.0.0</p>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>